  "id": "RAW_3f308687",
  "title": "Vercel 推出 Drains 功能：实现统一数据导出",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDE0Mjc4MA==&mid=2651258686&idx=4&sn=1b1fe814b03c904df17774cb766f371c",
  "date": "2025-10-14 04:03:00",
  "author": "InfoQ 中文",
  "siteName": "InfoQ 中文",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span>Daniel</span> <span>2025-10-14 12:03</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">浙江</span></p>\n  <p>Vercel 近日发布了 Vercel Drains 系统，用于将其平台上的可观测性数据导出至外部服务。</p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b3840e48&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FYriaiaJPb26VPLOOj6Awm7fo6UBejcKkIqib8EvTHe4uPR2NdYbC1lpbF61jrx41BSvicCibicBNa0zib40zq7N1MjGKA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"90\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"503629017\" data-ratio=\"0.15625\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=778e4015&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FYriaiaJPb26VPQqHC66RJFpttVIMWG83T3lWHahUD4bvhxlKSayjeV2ibvC5ydqklP9QHDPD3qHJM07TV3IfHstjA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></p>\n  <div style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;margin: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #919191;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin: 0;margin-top: 13px;padding-left: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者 | Daniel Dominguez </span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #919191;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin: 0;margin-top: 13px;padding-left: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">译者 | 马可薇 </span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">Vercel 近日发布了&nbsp;Vercel Drains&nbsp;系统，用于将其平台上的可观测性数据导出至外部服务。该功能将日志、分布式追踪、网站分析事件和性能指标统一整合到单一的流式传输机制中。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">这套系统覆盖多个来源的日志，包括运行时、构建、防火墙、函数和静态资源日志。它能导出符合&nbsp;OpenTelemetry&nbsp;标准的追踪数据、包含页面浏览量和自定义事件在内的网站分析数据，以及涵盖核心 Web 指标的&nbsp;Speed Insights&nbsp;数据。由于 Vercel 控制着从客户端到无服务器执行的完整请求路径，它会自动为日志条目添加 traceId 和 spanId，无需额外设置即可实现日志与追踪的关联。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">用户可通过两种方式配置：HTTP 排水孔，支持自定义端点，并提供灵活的格式、采样和签名选项；集成排水孔则是直接连接至各类可观测性服务商。导出的追踪数据遵循 OpenTelemetry 标准，可与&nbsp;Datadog、Honeycomb、Grafana Tempo&nbsp;和&nbsp;New Relic&nbsp;等系统无缝兼容。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">类似的竞品如&nbsp;AWS CloudWatch&nbsp;也可提供 AWS 生态系统中的日志收集、指标和追踪数据功能；Google Cloud Operations&nbsp;为 GCP 的工作负载提供结合了日志与追踪的类似管道；Azure Monitor&nbsp;则与 Application Insights 集成了以处理遥测数据。诸如&nbsp;Fluent Bit&nbsp;和&nbsp;OpenTelemetry Collector&nbsp;的开源方案虽然能提供了自定义管道，但需要单独的部署和管理。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">在社区讨论中，开发者们指出该功能无需额外埋点即可简化将 Vercel 项目接入现有监控技术栈的流程。软件开发者&nbsp;Virat Mankali&nbsp;评论道：</span></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">新一代可观测性方案发布！追踪、分析与日志的统一同步，加上一键导出？这对开发工作流绝对是革命性变革。</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">与此同时，Vercel 的产品经理&nbsp;Aparna Sinha&nbsp;分享道：</span></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">Vercel Drains 为用户供可在任意工具中使用的实时可观测数据，因为企业往往拥有众多需要不同数据维度的工具和团队。</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">业内人士也强调，对于目前需维护多个并行集成方案的团队而言，Drains 能够有效减少可观测性管道的碎片化。通过将指标、日志和追踪整合到统一的导出层，团队可以减少基础设施管理时间，更专注于数据分析。这种方式也让组织在不同可观测性服务商之间切换时，无需重新改造应用程序。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">每个团队和项目均可设置多个排水孔，相关配置可在 Vercel 仪表板的团队设置中完成。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">原文链接：</span></span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://www.infoq.com/news/2025/10/vercel-drains-observability/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.infoq.com/news/2025/10/vercel-drains-observability/</a></span></span></p>\n   <div style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;margin: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 14 []\">\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: #3f3f3f; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif; margin: 0; box-sizing: border-box;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-line; line-height: 27px; padding: 23px 8px 0 8px; margin: 0; color: #4a4a4a;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;font-style: italic;\">声明：本文为 InfoQ 翻译，未经许可禁止转载。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><strong data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant